Sentencas: Mathematical model based on the thermodynamic modeling of gaseous mixtures is developed for SOFC with internal steam reforming of methane.
Titulo: Thermodynamic modeling of the power plant based on the SOFC with internal steam reforming of methane

Sentencas: Macroscopic porous-electrode theory, including non-linear kinetics and gas-phase diffusion, is used to calculate the reforming reaction and the concentration polarization.
Titulo: Thermodynamic modeling of the power plant based on the SOFC with internal steam reforming of methane

Sentencas: Provided the data concerning properties and costs of materials the model is fit for wide range of parametric analysis of thermodynamic cycles including SOFC.
Titulo: Thermodynamic modeling of the power plant based on the SOFC with internal steam reforming of methane
